    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: 'This is a simple chat UI demo.

    The Canvas contains multiple Panels
    for different messages.

    They are disabled intentionally, so scripts can
    activate them.

    Canvas:IgnoreUiRaycastWhenInactive makes clicks ignore inactive
    panels.



    All users should use a UserId (to be found as friend).

    This
    message will go away at runtime.'
